===Verb===
'''ironing'''

# present participle of ''to [[iron]]''.

===Noun===
'''ironing''' ([[uncountable]])

# the act of pressing clothes with an iron.
#:''I hate ironing''.
# laundry having been washed and waiting to be ironed.
#:''I really should make a start on the ironing soon''.
# laundry having been recently ironed.
#:''I really should put the ironing away''.

